ent classes do. Analyses extended to the process of\nmouse nervous system development arrived at similar conclusions. Future studies\nwill be able to test whether this spatial organization of chromosomes\ncontributes to concerted gene expression.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jan 2019 16:21:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
